# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Voice Assistant — Environment Configuration Template
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to '.env' and fill in your keys:
#   cp .env.example .env
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── AI Backend Keys ───────────────────────────────────────────
# OpenAI API Key (Required if using OpenAI backend)
# Get a key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Google Gemini API Key (Required if using Gemini backend)
# Get a free key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# ── Hugging Face Configuration ────────────────────────────────
# Hugging Face User Access Token (Optional but recommended)
# Used to authenticate requests when downloading Whisper models.
# Prevents warnings and rate limits on downloading models.
# Get a free token at: https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
HF_TOKEN=your_hf_token_here
